{"tid":800103,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"ocamp 淫game 同大學hall 雞係唔係都市傳說黎？","createTime":"2018-08-30T15:03:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-31T17:44:56.000Z","uid":63913,"like":46,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"408444796f882718a880aea4baf24344d1e2d616","tid":800103,"uid":63913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T15:03:16.000Z","msg":"由year one 到final year，大大話話玩左七八個ocamp，有做組仔、組父同OC，但係都冇見過淫game。<br />\n<br />\nHall 都住足幾年，男女宿同男宿都住過，唔好話hall 雞，連hall鴨都冇見過。明明入大學前聽人講掛支螢光棒響門口做招牌，點解我搵左幾年都唔見？"},{"pid":"21155c6641fe60ab62d5eeac76fe1cb23c381247","tid":800103,"uid":143131,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T15:08:20.000Z","msg":"淫得既都上曬報<br />\n仲有人敢搞咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔驚個camp以後臭朵無人join咩"},{"pid":"ed728c38fe815108a10e3810818f1c14576db704","tid":800103,"uid":196924,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T15:09:37.000Z","msg":"個個都識講螢光棒做招牌, 咁又點會繼續用螢光棒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50f0c37907296356a68190ef5bdf019dfe019744","tid":800103,"uid":165232,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T15:11:30.000Z","msg":"可能大game無既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但夜晚房game一定有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d6730415a715b86483c5fe2af89b2b23c69356b","tid":800103,"uid":171509,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T15:11:51.000Z","msg":"你的樣子如何?"},{"pid":"f282aca7782446afcca9bc83ba1a1230f57bd599","tid":800103,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d6730415a715b86483c5fe2af89b2b23c69356b","tid":800103,"uid":171509,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T15:11:51.000Z","msg":"你的樣子如何?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T15:14:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"